flowchart TD

Contact[Contact Page /contato] --> Form[User fills Contact Form]
Form --> Validate{Client-side validation}
Validate -->|Valid| Submit[Submit]
Validate -->|Invalid| Errors[Inline errors + guidance]

Submit --> Feedback{Server response}
Feedback -->|Success| SuccessUI[Success message]
Feedback -->|Email failure but stored| SoftSuccess[Success message + internal logging]
Feedback -->|Hard failure| Retry[Retry guidance / alternative contact]
